<ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a> 接口的<code><strong>devicePixelRatio</strong></code>返回当前显示设备的<em>物理像素</em>分辨率与<em>CSS 像素</em>分辨率之比。 此值也可以解释为像素大小的比率：一个 CSS 像素的大小与一个物理像素的大小。 简单来说，它告诉浏览器应使用多少屏幕实际像素来绘制单个 CSS 像素。</p>\n\n<p>当处理标准显示器与 HiDPI 或 Retina 显示器之间的差异时，这很有用，后者使用更多的屏幕像素绘制相同的对象，从而获得更清晰的图像。</p>\n\n<p>您可以使用<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/matchMedia\" title=\"window.matchMedia()\"><code>window.matchMedia()</code></a> 检查<code>devicePixelRatio</code>的值是否发生更改（例如，如果用户将窗口拖动到带有 不同的像素密度）。 请参阅<a href=\"#监视屏幕分辨率或缩放级别的更改\">下面的例子</a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em><var>value</var></em> = window.devicePixelRatio;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"值value","title":"值 Value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>一个双精度浮点值，指示显示器的物理像素分辨率与 CSS 像素分辨率之比。 值 1 表示经典 96 DPI（在某些平台上为 76 DPI）显示，而对于 HiDPI / Retina 显示屏则期望值为 2。 在异常低分辨率的显示器中，或更常见的是，当屏幕的像素深度比简单地将 96 或 76 DPI 的标准分辨率提高一倍时，可能还会返回其他值。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"在_<canvas>_中更正分辨率","title":"在&nbsp;<code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code>&nbsp;中更正分辨率","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a>可能在视网膜屏幕上显得太模糊。 使用<code>window.devicePixelRatio</code>确定应添加多少额外的像素密度以使图像更清晰。</p>\n\n<h4 id=\"html\">HTML</h4>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;canvas id=\"canvas\"&gt;&lt;/canvas&gt;</pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"javascript\">JavaScript</h4>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">var canvas = document.getElementById('canvas');\nvar ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');\n\n// Set display size (css pixels).\nvar size = 200;\ncanvas.style.width = size + \"px\";\ncanvas.style.height = size + \"px\";\n\n// Set actual size in memory (scaled to account for extra pixel density).\nvar scale = window.devicePixelRatio; // Change to 1 on retina screens to see blurry canvas.\ncanvas.width = Math.floor(size * scale);\ncanvas.height = Math.floor(size * scale);\n\n// Normalize coordinate system to use css pixels.\nctx.scale(scale, scale);\n\nctx.fillStyle = \"#bada55\";\nctx.fillRect(10, 10, 300, 300);\nctx.fillStyle = \"#ffffff\";\nctx.font = '18px Arial';\nctx.textAlign = 'center';\nctx.textBaseline = 'middle';\n\nvar x = size / 2;\nvar y = size / 2;\n\nvar textString = \"I love MDN\";\nctx.fillText(textString, x, y);</pre>","titleAsText":"在 <canvas> 中更正分辨率"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sect1","title":"<img alt=\"This image describe the impact of different value on retina display. \" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/15023/devicePixelRation%20Diff..png\" loading=\"lazy\">","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"监视屏幕分辨率或缩放级别的更改","title":"监视屏幕分辨率或缩放级别的更改","isH3":true,"content":"<p>在此示例中，我们将设置一个媒体查询并观看它以查看设备分辨率何时更改，以便我们可以检查<code>devicePixelRatio</code>的值来处理所需的任何更新。</p>\n\n<h4 id=\"javascript_2\">JavaScript</h4>\n\n<p>JavaScript 代码创建媒体查询，以监控设备分辨率并在每次更改时检查<code>devicePixelRatio</code>的值。</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">let pixelRatioBox = document.querySelector(\".pixel-ratio\");\nlet mqString = `(resolution: ${window.devicePixelRatio}dppx)`;\n\nconst updatePixelRatio = () =&gt; {\n  let pr = window.devicePixelRatio;\n  let prString = (pr * 100).toFixed(0);\n  pixelRatioBox.innerText = `${prString}% (${pr.toFixed(2)})`;\n}\n\nupdatePixelRatio();\n\nmatchMedia(mqString).addListener(updatePixelRatio);\n</pre>\n\n<p>字符串<code>mqString</code>设置为媒体查询本身。 媒体查询以<code>(resolution: 1dppx)</code>（对于标准显示）或<code>(resolution: 2dppx)</code>（对于 Retina / HiDPI 显示）开始，检查当前显示分辨率是否与每个像素<code>px</code>的实际设备像素点匹配。</p>\n\n<p><code>updatePixelRatio()</code>函数获取<code>devicePixelRatio</code>的当前值，然后将<code>pixelRatioBox</code>的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/innerText\" title=\"innerText\"><code>innerText</code></a>设置为一个字符串，该字符串同时显示百分比和原始十进制值比率，最多两位小数。</p>\n\n<p>然后，调用<code>updatePixelRatio()</code>函数一次以显示起始值，然后使用<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/matchMedia\" title=\"matchMedia()\"><code>matchMedia()</code></a> 和 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\" title=\"addEventListener()\"><code>addEventListener()</code></a>来将<code>updatePixelRatio()</code>设置为<code>change</code>事件的处理程序。</p>\n\n<h4 id=\"html_2\">HTML</h4>\n\n<p>HTML 将创建包含说明的框和将显示当前像素比率信息的<code>pixel-ratio</code>&nbsp;框。</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;div class=\"container\"&gt;\n  &lt;div class=\"inner-container\"&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;This example demonstrates the effect of zooming the page in\n       and out (or moving it to a screen with a different scaling\n       factor) on the value of the property &lt;code&gt;Window.devicePixelRatio&lt;/code&gt;.\n       Try it and watch what happens!&lt;/p&gt;\n  &lt;/div&gt;\n    &lt;div class=\"pixel-ratio\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;</pre>\n\n<details><summary>\n<h4 id=\"css\">CSS</h4>\n</summary>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">body {\n  font: 22px arial, sans-serif;\n}\n\n.container {\n  top: 2em;\n  width: 22em;\n  height: 14em;\n  border: 2px solid #22d;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  padding: 0;\n  background-color: #a9f;\n}\n\n.inner-container {\n  padding: 1em 2em;\n  text-align: justify;\n  text-justify: auto;\n}\n\n.pixel-ratio {\n  position: relative;\n  margin: auto;\n  height: 1.2em;\n  text-align: right;\n  bottom: 0;\n  right: 1em;\n  font-weight: bold;\n}</pre>\n</details>\n\n<h4 id=\"result\">Result</h4>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Monitoring screen resolution or zoom level changes sample\" id=\"frame_monitoring_screen_resolution_or_zoom_level_changes\" width=\"100%\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/devicePixelRatio/_sample_.monitoring_screen_resolution_or_zoom_level_changes.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-view/#dom-window-devicepixelratio\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM) View Module<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Window.devicePixelRatio</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Window.devicePixelRatio","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/devicePixelRatio/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The compatibility table on this page is generated from structured data. If you'd like to contribute to the data, please check out&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data</a>&nbsp;and send us a pull request.</p>\n\n<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries\">Media queries</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media_queries\">Using media queries</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/resolution\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">CSS&nbsp;resolution&nbsp;media query (en-US)</a></li>\n <li></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"summary"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"<img alt=\"This image describe the impact of different value on retina display. \" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/15023/devicePixelRation%20Diff..png\" loading=\"lazy\">","id":"sect1"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"Window 接口的devicePixelRatio返回当前显示设备的物理像素分辨率与CSS 像素分辨率之比。 此值也可以解释为像素大小的比率：一个 CSS 像素的大小与一个物理像素的大小。 简单来说，它告诉浏览器应使用多少屏幕实际像素来绘制单个 CSS 像素。","popularity":0.0008,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window.devicePixelRatio","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Window.devicePixelRatio","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Window.devicePixelRatio","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Window.devicePixelRatio","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Window.devicePixelRatio","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Window.devicePixelRatio","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/window/devicepixelratio","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/window/devicepixelratio/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"Window"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/devicePixelRatio","title":"Window.devicePixelRatio"}],"pageTitle":"Window.devicePixelRatio - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}